  "detailed_description": "Kill your enemies in style<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2268220/extras/fe3610c05b181ff12699f61cdcf301bc.avif?t=1677814302\" width=600 height=304 /></span><br><br>You hear their screams but you are not afraid, shoot them down to score. Play against hordes of zombies while trying to beat them in<br>a soccer game. Be strategic and collect lots of ammo. <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2268220/extras/bfd3987a6fa14c123cfa944800869d57.avif?t=1677814302\" width=600 height=326 /></span><br><br>So what if there are giant zombies. You still have one goal in mind, win a championship. Play giants against armies of massive zombies that you are still able to take down with your weapons. <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2268220/extras/c30d92301759be2c2c0133cc1b4470de.avif?t=1677814302\" width=600 height=326 /></span>",
